just disappeared like that.

00:38.690 --> 00:40.257
We're all praying
for his safe return, of course,

00:40.301 --> 00:43.826
-just not until enrollment
closes. -JESS: Oh, my God.

00:43.869 --> 00:45.610
Wait. Didn't you guys already
look at a preschool?

00:45.654 --> 00:47.047
[scoffs]
You mean Triangles?

00:47.090 --> 00:48.265
[chickens clucking]

00:48.309 --> 00:51.312
Okay.

00:51.355 --> 00:53.618
-Ew.
-Chicken.

00:53.662 --> 00:55.185
-Hmm? -I made eye contact
with the chicken.

00:55.229 --> 00:56.447
He knows
that I had eggs for breakfast.

00:56.491 --> 00:58.188
Take her. Take the pretty one.

00:58.232 --> 01:00.277
-I don't think that a chicken
cares that you had eggs. -No!

01:00.321 --> 01:01.713
I mean, I kind of
liked Triangles.

01:01.757 --> 01:04.151
Besides, are we really
Lillypads people?

01:04.194 --> 01:06.196
-Yes. -I hope not.
That kind of competitive,

01:06.240 --> 01:08.851
overpriced private school,
B dash, dash,

01:08.894 --> 01:12.289
dash, dash, dash, dash,
dash... T is the reason why

01:12.333 --> 01:15.118
I got out of teaching
in the first place.

01:15.162 --> 01:16.163
What did happen
at Banyon Canyon?

01:16.206 --> 01:17.512
Yeah, what did happen
at Banyon Canyon?

01:17.555 --> 01:19.079
You know I can't
discuss that until

01:19.122 --> 01:20.645
one of four
civil lawsuits is settled.

01:20.689 --> 01:23.300
-I know, but what...
-No further questions. You guys,

01:23.344 --> 01:25.694
this is crazy. Look at this
beautiful, impressionable child.

01:25.737 --> 01:28.131
Lillypads is the key
to Ruth's future.

01:28.175 --> 01:30.873
If she gets into Lillypads,
she gets into Willows.

01:30.916 --> 01:32.396
If she gets into Willows,
she gets into Harvard.

01:32.440 --> 01:33.702
