hippie-dippie mishegas

01:57.508 --> 01:59.249
ruin Ruth's future.

01:59.293 --> 02:02.470
-[gasps]
-This child is a genius.

02:02.513 --> 02:04.254
Yay! [grunts]

02:04.298 --> 02:06.343
-Oh!
-RUTH: Whoa.

02:06.387 --> 02:07.779
She does this all the time.
Just give her a minute.

02:07.823 --> 02:09.390
-She'll come to.
-Yeah.

02:09.433 --> 02:11.174
-I'm okay! -[chuckles]
There she is. -There she is.

02:11.218 --> 02:13.089
-[Ruth thuds] -Oh! Whoa.
-Oh, my God. -Okay, all right.

