02:21.445 --> 02:22.577
NICK:
Hey, Jess.

02:22.620 --> 02:24.492
-Hi.
-I'm off to the bar to write.

02:24.535 --> 02:26.450
This is the first day
working on my new idea

02:26.494 --> 02:28.365
